race.description: Scobie Beasley & Stuart Anderson Mdn Plate (C1)
race.comment: HOT ONE (8) caught the eye last start at Echuca when coming from a long way back to finish midfield, only 1.6L away from the winner. Draws to take much closer order from the inside pillar and gets in well at the weights with the claim. Can get the job done. CARAVANSERAI (3) stuck on gamely into second at Moruya over the same trip. Best figures stack up and he looks a key danger. STAR EMPIRE (5) has missed the frame at his last couple but could improve sharply with the blinkers going on first time. Keeping safe. Race falls away somewhat after this trio post scratchings. PIMPERNEL (4) next elect to round out the exotics.
